ith the holes more localized near\nthe node in the antiferromagnetic spin order. In both cases, we find that the\nwavelength in the charge correlations is consistent with so-called filled\nstripes in the pure Hubbard model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 Dec 2021 22:59:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 15 Mar 2022 04:12:41 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 30 Mar 2022 01:02:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-31"}
